                              'HoloH' 1.01

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  @{" HoloH " link play} is a Workbench game where the goal is to move coloured
shapes so they fall in a hole that is located in the center of the
play area. If 2 or more shapes of the same type consecutively fall
in the hole, you will get much more points...

  One important thing to remember: do NOT move shapes of the same
type next to each other, either horizontally or vertically, as
that would end the game.

  Have fun!

